comments: Dort (OKC) is moving alongside Millsap's (DEN) path and maintains a legal guarding position at the end of the drive.

Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Horford (OKC).
Horford (OKC) places an arm against Murray (DEN) during the screen, but he does not move through his space and dislodge him from his position as he disengages.
Murray (DEN) is already in Horford's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Horford (OKC) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Jokic (DEN) and Horford (OKC) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Murray (DEN) is already in Horford's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
